RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.Branch_Code, a.Branch_Name, Today AS Branch_Date, Decode(c.End_Of_Input,'N','TI','T','POSTEOTI','F','POSTEOFI','E','POSTEOD','B','POSTBOD') AS Curr_State FROM Sttm_Core_Branch a, Sttm_Dates B, Sttm_core_Branch_status c where a.Branch_Code NOT IN (SELECT Branch_Code FROM Aetb_Eoc_Branches WHERE Eoc_Status IN ('N', 'W', 'P')) AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' AND a.Branch_Code = b.Branch_Code AND a.Branch_Code = c.Branch_Code
SELECT GROUP_CODE, GROUP_DESCRIPTION FROM AETM_EOC_GROUP_MASTER WHERE ONCE_AUTH ='Y' AND RECORD_STAT ='O'
